Package com.fudan.sw.dsa.project2.bean

Class Edge

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fudan.sw.dsa.project2.bean.Edge
  • public class Edge
extends java.lang.Object
    The abstraction of the edges in the graph. The weight indicates the running time of the subway between two stations, the two vertices variable shows which vertex it is connecting and the line String is the name of the edge.
    Author:
    Wang, Chen
